name: Shut up or die
description: hungry of authority and victory is human nature from the era of Adam until now, glory and satisfying worldly desires. every ruler has a privilege to suppress you weak, treats everything like a slave, this painting is a continuation of the concept of authoritarianism and unfair laws, through this painting makes satire and communication messages from real events, that the freedom of every human being is not completely free, many falsehoods are many secret things made by some humans, to cover the rottenness and filth of their actions
